               <p>SARAH LOWNS. I am <rs id="t18291203-185-viclabel955" type="occupation">single</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18291203-185-victim1177 t18291203-185-viclabel955"></join>, and <rs id="t18291203-185-viclabel956" type="occupation">keep a little haberdasher's-shop</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18291203-185-victim1177 t18291203-185-viclabel956"></join> - I heard these shoes cut from the door, and went to the door - I saw the prisoner running, called Stop thief! and he was taken.</p>
               <p>THOMAS PATTEN. I saw the prisoner run, and drop these shoes.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I did it through distress; I was obliged to sell my shirt for victuals - the parish would do nothing for me.</p>
